    <studytitle>Three Techniques for Establishing Component Alignment in Total Knee Reconstruction: A Randomised Clinical Trial</studytitle>
    <scientifictitle>A comparison of extramedullary, intramedullary and computer-assisted surgery alignment techniques for establishing component alignment in total knee reconstruction: a randomised clinical trial</scientifictitle>
